Rahi is a wildflower that was watered by rain and fed by sun. Growing up, she climbed mountains, swam across the rivers, devoured what tempted her, and wrote her experiences in regional newspapers and magazines. Later cherished for making travel and food content on YouTube, she connected with people at different places, with varied occupations, opinions, and life stories. Being a state-level gymnast and dancer, and an NCC cadet, the extracurriculars were never extras for her. A silver medalist at her degree college is now also a dropout from her PG. [rahi_runs](https://www.instagram.com/rahi_runs/) being the username on the Instagram, she also ran from her corporate job with a laptop and a Wi-Fi router (not really). Here she is, trying to connect with you all with her crazy and surprising stories in the form of articles and voiceovers.&nbsp;\
\
